  "name": "13) Winter Phase (Both)",
  "_id": "NKQVeB00DO4RfHEj",
  "pages": [
    {
      "sort": 100000,
      "name": "Winter Phase",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "JClE8n4rcuXssKLs",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>Activating the Winter Phase is controlled by the GM from the GM Tools.</p><p>Once Winter Phase is turned on there will be an extra tab visible on your Character Sheet. An History entry is added to your @UUID[Compendium.Pendragon.instructions.JournalEntry.b5d7Ha8LOeLSNvul.JournalEntryPage.8390AvE66aRvM5fJ]{Events Tab} with this year's glory.</p><p>When the Winter Phase is turned off the game year increases by one and so your character's age will automatically increase by 1 year.</p><p>There are many steps to a Winter Phase. You can do everything manually or some stages have been automated for you. Given that a character can die (in Childbirth or due to aging) we appreciate you may want to makes the rolls yourself.</p><p>The stages of the Winter Phase are:</p><ul><li><p>@UUID[.SATAFmPjcQbxdClZ] (manual)</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.TkC0R47aztAeBTQu] (manual)</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.jnbbfQEU7hcwV3Ah]</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.RrrOlH0FVuoe2fox]</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.F3ATfUdHvTCV5ZE6]</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.65FI8fOChF1PF07n]</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.dtFFRERr0gt3dI8V]</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.y70FF7IdgRTnHweV]</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.Q3jZfR6tyGC4Dk4U] - this is fully automated</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.7w2QQBimHJ8DcuNu]</p></li><li><p>@UUID[.PzONb0J36K4pjM49]</p></li></ul><p>As each step is completed (if using the automated process) then a tick will appear next to the step name and clicking on the step will no longer do anything.</p>"
      },
