    {
      "sort": 300000,
      "name": "Training",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "y70FF7IdgRTnHweV",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">There are two options under the training banner - you will only be able to choose one per Winter Phase</span></p><ul style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 1.5em;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\"><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">to improve a statistics a single point (this allows you to raise a characteristic, increase/decrease a passion or trait and raise a skill that is already 15 or higher)</span></p></li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">spread training across skills, lets you spend 6 points across skills that are 14 or lower</span></p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">Once you've selected the appropriate option a pop up box will appear listing the statistics you can train that are relevant to your option (e.g. choosing the improve single point option will not show skills below 15 score).</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">Only skills, traits, passions on the character sheet will be shown so if you want to train a new skill for example add it to the character sheet first.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">Click on the up and down arrows to improve or reduce a statistic.Â  There are maximum and minimum values in line with the rules that limit what you can change (e.g. trying to improve a skill that is already 20 will do nothing, or trying to reduce a passion below 1 also does nothing).</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">For traits only the main trait is shown, not the opposing trait. To increase the opposing trait simply click the down arrow for the main trait. E.g. to increase Lazy, select to reduce Energetic.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">If you have chosen the multiple point options then the grid will show you the new score and you can remove these points by clicking the opposite arrow (e.g. if you raised First Aid by 3 points, clicking the down arrow reduces the spend to 2 points).</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">The pop up box willÂ close as soon as you have spent the relevant number of points. A history event will be added showing your training.</span></p>"
      },
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
