    {
      "sort": 400000,
      "name": "Prestige Awards",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "7w2QQBimHJ8DcuNu",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">The number in brackets is the number of prestige reward you have to spend. Clicking on this option will give you a pop up box listing all the statistics you can change. Click on the relevant up or down arrow to select that item.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">For traits only the main trait is shown, not the opposing trait. To increase the opposing trait simply click the down arrow for the main trait. E.g. to increase Lazy, select to reduce Energetic.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">Only skills, traits, passions on the character sheet will be shown so if you want to train a new skill for example add it to the character sheet first.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">The pop up box will close as soon as you click an up or down arrow. A history event will be added and the number of Rewards will be reduced.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">You can repeat this step if you have multiple reward points to spend.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;margin:0.5em 0px;color:rgb(25, 24, 19);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:15.75px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text\">Note</strong>: The GM can edit the number of points you have spent if the character sheet is unlocked.</span></p><p>If you want to spend Prestige on Child Birth rolls that is done through the next step @UUID[.PzONb0J36K4pjM49]</p>"
      },
