      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>This step is automated.</p><p>Combat and special horses must make a roll to survive the year. </p><p>In some cases you will have a Horsemanship roll made for you as part of the horse survival.  This does not give an XP check at this time.</p><p>Horses can survive, loose stats, hit points  etc or die</p><p>If horses die <span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">you are given the option to delete the items manually or let the system do it.</span></p><p></p>"
      },
